name: New Jersey Secretary of State Tahesha Way
tweet: New Jersey voters- The polls will close at 8 pm. If you are on line to vote at 8 pm, stay in line and you will be able to vote, no matter how long it takes.

name: New Jersey Secretary of State Tahesha Way
tweet: Happy Election Day, New Jersey! If you haven't voted yet, you have until 8 pm to vote today. Find your polling location here:  https://t.co/rkUNRF0wTb  https://t.co/AWXQ1lJAqK

name: New Jersey Secretary of State Tahesha Way
tweet: If you requested a vote by mail (VBM) ballot for this election, you have until November 2 to return it via mail, at one of your county's secure ballot dropboxes, or at your County Board of Elections. You CANNOT return your VBM ballot at a polling location.  https://t.co/WgjPn6cijT
